hcc_text: Van Wyck Exwy Service Road West is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Queens)
info: At Van Wyck Exwy Service Road West at 111th Avenue and Lincoln Street, there were 3 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
